## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a7c2c-102">默认情况下， <xref:System.Object> 类型参数作为类型进行封送处理 `VARIANT` ，其中对象类型确定的 `VARTYPE` 值 `VARIANT` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a7c2c-102">By default, <xref:System.Object> type arguments are marshaled as a `VARIANT` type, where the object type determines the `VARTYPE` value of the `VARIANT`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a7c2c-103"><xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper>类型必须作为类型进行 <xref:System.Object> 封送处理 `VARIANT` `VT_ERROR` ，否则类型 <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> 将作为整数封送。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a7c2c-103">The <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type must to be passed as an <xref:System.Object> type to be marshaled as a `VARIANT` of type `VT_ERROR`, otherwise the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.ErrorWrapper> type is marshaled as an integer.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="a7c2c-104">下表说明了使用平台调用对本机函数进行的封送处理。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a7c2c-104">The following table illustrates marshaling in a managed call to a native function, using platform invoke.</span></span>  
  
